{"tid":415241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[叫雞唔比錢］AV粉絲向偶像Twitter說睇免費片，女優傷心難過","createTime":"2017-09-26T23:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T03:03:32.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a769eef8ecf67f5ee768f3949c1e5f5b17c812ca","tid":415241,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:25:58.000Z","msg":"日本AV產業盛行，帶來的收益相當可觀，不過盜版影片猖獗也是片廠的另一大隱憂，AV女優辛苦下海拍攝的片子卻淪為盜版商的生財工具，其中也透露了AV女優不為人知的辛酸血淚。<br />\n<br />\n日本AV女優加藤綾野在個人推特上表示，近日得知一名粉絲聲稱很喜歡她的作品，不過卻自爆總是只看「無料」，從盜版網站取得非法免費的影片，令加藤綾野一點也開心不起來，且不禁質疑，這樣的粉絲倒底算不算是真的粉絲呢？<br />\n<br />\n文章一推出，立刻掀起一陣熱議，網友們紛紛留言表示，「真正的粉絲應該是要支持正版，把片子買回家慢慢欣賞吧」、「這樣不能稱為粉絲啊」、「在偶像面前這樣說真的很傷人耶」、「支持正版」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.nownews.com/news/2613433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F2613433&d=ET79mwu14G5d3JvAXnBCiP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0b753b60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.nownews.com/news/2613433</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/072544_ebc47a971e676aad57b9dcb40576f885.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F072544_ebc47a971e676aad57b9dcb40576f885.jpg&h=451c3625&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/072546_3fa672af3af529484c4f07690fc6a4ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F072546_3fa672af3af529484c4f07690fc6a4ce.jpg&h=de44570b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/072547_0a1b4d5e543d416f0c4d6fc51f189341.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F072547_0a1b4d5e543d416f0c4d6fc51f189341.jpg&h=487bac25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/072547_cdb73dc45519164b4080c23b8c8cb814.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F072547_cdb73dc45519164b4080c23b8c8cb814.jpg&h=c79716da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好無品"},{"pid":"cb968bda519e6cbaeaf69d58344539ff7786bac2","tid":415241,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:28:43.000Z","msg":"自己知就算啦，仲要刺激人"},{"pid":"b1aa9af427b3b2ca6e0276bd8901217e36ea3783","tid":415241,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5194cffeeaf405913f582955258d63226b66f869","tid":415241,"uid":4210,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:49:26.000Z","msg":"咁樣衰 請我都唔睇"},{"pid":"911507ebfa3bf659bcfdb876e28305224bb1d3fb","tid":415241,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:03:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}